# Icon

A React implementation of the IDS icon font, using SVG components.

⚠️ **Deprecation warning** ⚠️

This component has been deprecated and is no longer maintained. We recommend using the `@design-systems/icons` package instead.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/icon
```

```tsx
import { Icon } from '@ids-ts/icon';
```

## Props

> **Deprecated** — Use `@design-systems/icons` instead.

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `name` | `string` | Yes | Icon name from the IDS icon set. |
| `size` | `'small' \| 'medium' \| 'large'` | No | Icon size. |
| `color` | `string` | No | Icon color override. |

## Token Usage

### Color

**icon** — Icon fill and stroke colors
- `--color-icon-accent`
- `--color-icon-complementary`
- `--color-icon-disabled`

### Size

**icon** — Standard icon dimensions

## Usage Patterns

### Basic

```tsx
({ fill, size }) => (
  <CircleCheckIcon data-automation-id="basic" size={size} fill={fill} />
)
```

